.SH NAME
srt \- sort lines in a file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B srt
.I input_file output_file
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sort lines in a file alphabetically.
.SH OPTIONS
None.
.SH EXAMPLES
srt unsorted.txt sorted.txt
